name: Father Code Token
description: The Father Code Token (FCD) is a utility token of the premium brand Father Code. It provides access to exclusive products, discounts, NFTs, and the brand's legendary 'Treasure Hunt,' a multi-level quest encoded with music videos, packaging, and secret QR codes. Viral TikTok content and song lyrics serve as hidden clues. FCD holders can uncover a portion of the mystery, which may lead to obtaining a gold bar, a legendary belt, and even a stake in the brand itself. FCD is not just a symbol of traditional values, but a key to prosperity and a story that will become a legend for decades to come.
